comments.body:
Could turn this into:
```suggestion
std::string NetworkErrorString(int err)
{
#ifdef WIN32
    return Win32ErrorString(err);
#else
    // On BSD sockets implementations, NetworkErrorString is the same as SysErrorString.
    return SysErrorString(err);
#endif
}
```

